<div align="left"><p>Congratulations on starting a new business. Here is a link to your home page: <a href="https://www.sos.state.co.us/biz/BusinessEntityDetail.do?masterFileId=20261676445">https://www.sos.state.co.us/biz/BusinessEntityDetail.do?masterFileId=20261676445</a>. On your home page, you can get a copy of your filed document or a Good Standing certificate. You can also see other information for your entity.</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>This is an automatically generated email. If you would like to contact our office, please send an email to <a href="mailto:business@coloradosos.gov">business@coloradosos.gov</a> or call 303-894-2200 and press 2.</p>
<p>If you would like to unsubscribe from this email notification service, visit our website, <a href="https://coloradosos.gov/">coloradosos.gov</a>, select "Business Organizations" in the menu on the left, then click on "Email Notifications".</p><br />
